   <body>
      <p>Power Invoice Generation ​​​​​​​for Salesforce Billing has the following limitations:</p>
      <ul>
         <li>Customers can only generate documents from the objects within the Salesforce Billing installed package (those with the <i>blng</i> prefix).</li>
         <li>Word and HTML Email are the only supported template types.</li>
         <li>Email and PDF are the only output file types.</li>
         <li>Up to 1,000 invoices per month.</li>
      </ul>
